SUMMARY:Taiwan Studies Initiative Milk Tea Month: Bubble Tea Workshop
DESCRIPTION:Join the IU Taiwan Studies Initiative and NTU Huayu BEST Prog
 ram for this year's Taiwan Day cultural event! During the workshop\, part
 icipants will watch a demonstration of how bubble tea gets made. During t
 he reception\, participants will move to the Global Lounge to assemble th
 eir own bubble tea\, learn more about Taiwanese tea culture\, and have th
 e chance to win prizes.
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p><span data-teams="true">Join the IU Taiwa
 n Studies Initiative and NTU Huayu BEST Program for this year's Taiwan Da
 y cultural event! During the workshop\, participants will watch a demonst
 ration of how bubble tea gets made. During the reception\, participants w
 ill move to the Global Lounge to assemble their own bubble tea\, learn mo
 re about Taiwanese tea culture\, and have the chance to win prizes.</span
 ></p>
