 allation that transforms the museum into a vibrant\, crocheted\, underwat
 er ecosystem inspired by Indonesia's spectacular coral reefs. Explore col
 orful coral reefs\, playful fish\, and fantastical sea creatures â€” all 
 meticulously hand-knit and crocheted. <a href="https://artmuseum.indiana.
 edu/exhibitions/current/_feature-exhibitions/2026-02-07-mulyana-vital-eco
 systems.html">Read more about this featured exhibition.</a></p><p><i>Step
